                <a href="#"><strong style="font-size:16px;">Stripe's quiet shift to becoming an infrastructure company</strong></a><br/>
                <span style="color:#737373;font-size:14px;">Stratechery · 12 min</span>
              </td>
            </tr>
            <tr class="read-item">
              <td width="40" valign="top"><span class="read-num">02</span></td>
              <td valign="top">
                <a href="#"><strong style="font-size:16px;">Why the post-Substack newsletter is bundled again</strong></a><br/>
                <span style="color:#737373;font-size:14px;">Platformer · 8 min</span>
              </td>
            </tr>
            <tr class="read-item">
              <td width="40" valign="top"><span class="read-num">03</span></td>
              <td valign="top">
                <a href="#"><strong style="font-size:16px;">The compiler is the new framework</strong></a><br/>
                <span style="color:#737373;font-size:14px;">Brian Lovin's blog · 6 min</span>
              </td>
            </tr>
          </table>
        </mj-text>
      </mj-column>
    </mj-section>

    <!-- Tool -->
    <mj-section background-color="#fafaf7" padding="32px 48px 0 48px">
      <mj-column>
        <mj-divider border-color="#ececec" border-width="1px" padding="0 0 24px 0" />
        <mj-text mj-class="kicker" padding="0 0 10px 0">One tool I'm using</mj-text>
        <mj-text padding="0 0 8px 0"><span class="h2">Raycast Notes</span></mj-text>
        <mj-text color="#525252" font-size="15px" padding="0 0 12px 0">I keep trying to replace Apple Notes. Raycast Notes is the first one that's stuck — it lives behind a global shortcut, doesn't ask me to organize anything, and syncs faster than I can context-switch.</mj-text>
        <mj-text font-size="14px"><a href="#">raycast.com/notes</a></mj-text>
      </mj-column>
    </mj-section>

    <!-- Quote -->
    <mj-section background-color="#fafaf7" padding="40px 48px 0 48px">
      <mj-column>
        <mj-divider border-color="#ececec" border-width="1px" padding="0 0 28px 0" />
        <mj-text mj-class="serif" font-style="italic" font-size="22px" line-height="1.4" color="#0a0a0a" padding="0 0 12px 0">"The best way to predict the future is to invent it."</mj-text>
        <mj-text color="#737373" font-size="14px" padding="0">— Alan Kay</mj-text>
      </mj-column>
    </mj-section>

    <!-- Sign-off -->
    <mj-section background-color="#fafaf7" padding="40px 48px 40px 48px">
      <mj-column>
        <mj-divider border-color="#0a0a0a" border-width="1px" padding="0 0 28px 0" />
        <mj-text color="#525252" font-size="15px" padding="0 0 8px 0">Thanks for reading. Forward to a friend who'd like it, or:</mj-text>
